    </para>
    <para id="import-auto-id5455567"><emphasis effect="bold">Time (When/Length):  </emphasis>The program is about an hour in length and is presented at least twice prior to the beginning of each athletic season.</para>
    <para id="import-auto-id5473597"><emphasis effect="bold">Location (Space):  </emphasis>McQuaid Jesuit auditorium and/or cafeteria.</para>
    <para id="import-auto-id4727574"><emphasis effect="bold">Accountability/Assessment:  </emphasis>Parents of athletes are required to attend in order for their sons to be eligible to compete.</para>
